---
title: Chorizo, Mushroom & Cheese Shakshuka with Sourdough & Salad | Serves 2
description: Take a bite of Middle Eastern decadence with our chorizo shakshuka and crunchy sourdough. Enjoy the taste of our creamy crumbly cheese combined with chorizo and mushrooms mixed into a rich tomato sauce. With everything cooked in one pan, all you need to do is add your eggs and enjoy!

